Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我还有一些线索\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have some more material.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,‎看上去你必须查明并确定\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It seems you will have to identify and secure
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他死亡的准确位置\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}the precise location of his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我是说 ‎地板上的准确位置\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}By which I mean the exact spot on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎告诉瓦尼 有确切证据表明\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And tell Varney there is definitely evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:03:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,塔哥维斯特的宫廷手里有一面传送镜\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}of a transmission mirror in the possession of the court at Targoviste.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我在设法追查更多的信息\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm working to track down more information.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎卡米拉的私人珍藏\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}From Carmilla's private stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,‎现在 给我看看你说过的地狱地图\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Now show me the map of hell you told me about,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不然我就告诉她 ‎你对她的鞋动了手脚\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}or I'll tell her what you've been doing with her shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,‎早上好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎晚上好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎该死\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你做坏了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You broke it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这些钢胚有一半是坏的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Half these billets are bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你的吸血鬼铁匠没有按我的要求做\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Your vampire blacksmiths didn't follow my specifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:04:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,‎蹩脚的工匠总是归罪于吸血鬼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}A bad workman always blames his vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你没有别的事可做吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Don't you have anything better to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,‎现在没有\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,‎斯崔格和莫拉娜离开好几个星期了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Striga and Morana have been away for weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎勘查将要吞并的领土\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}surveying the territories to be annexed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎卡米拉在画地图\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Carmilla is drawing maps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,‎看来 一切事情都需要外交的‎时代\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It seems the time when diplomacy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎已经过去了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}was required for anything has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你觉得无聊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Ah, so you're bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不 ‎你是在担心\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No. You're worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎闭嘴\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Shush.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎丽诺尔 她们在排挤你吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Lenore, are they sidelining you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎她们没有…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不是那样的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎至少她们不会那样想\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Or, at least, they wouldn't think of it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们的生活进入了新阶段\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Our lives have entered a new phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎外交 谈判\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Diplomacy, negotiations,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这些已经成为了历史\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}these are things of the past now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也让你成为了历史\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Which makes you a thing of the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这让你很困扰\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and that is bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,‎听着...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,‎卡米拉计划给我们争取\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Carmilla's plan buys us security
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎未来几百年的保障\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}for hundreds of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我是经历过战争的孩子 赫克托\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm a child of war, Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我就出生在这样的城堡里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I was born in a castle like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎英国士兵嘴里叼着刀子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}My parents died when English soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,爬上马桶滑槽 杀死了我父母\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}climbed up the toilet chutes with knives in their teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我在五岁前见惯了战争\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'd seen enough war before I was five years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎此后的生活也没有变好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and life didn't get better after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我绝不会心安理得地认为\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But I will never be comfortable
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎结束战争最好的方法就是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}with the idea that the best way to end war
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎杀掉大部分人 把其他人关进牢房\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}is to kill most of the people and cage the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你是外交官\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, you are a diplomat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎要是你不做那把该死的锤子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, none of this will matter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎就不会这么闹心了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}if you don't make that bloody hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎为什么你不能像巫师一样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Why can't you just wave your fingers like a wizard
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎挥动手指就能起死回生\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to raise the dead, or whatever?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎锻造师借助工具来工作\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The forgemaster works through an instrument.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这可能是我听过的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That may be the worst justification
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎男人要握着小鸡鸡最差劲的借口了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}for a man holding his penis that I've ever heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我的天啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我都200岁了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I am 200 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎听着...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我是锻造师\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am a forgemaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这名字不是我发明的 好吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I didn't invent the name, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们就是这么叫我们的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's just what they call us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:06:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‎通过工具才能把魔法集中起来施展\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And the magic has to be focused through an instrument,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,‎就像用笛子吹气一样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}like breath being pushed through a flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这个解释没什么用\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This isn't getting any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我需要该死的锤子 这个解释行吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I need the bloody hammer. Is that better?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那就用该死的锤子啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So use a bloody hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这里肯定有上千把该死的锤子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There must be a thousand bloody hammers around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不 一定要特别的锤子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No, it's got to be special.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你的特别的锤子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Your special hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你够了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Would you stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一定要从头做起\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It has to be made from scratch,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,用非常特别的方式\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}in a very particular way,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎否则就不管用\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}or else it won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎就像没有孔的笛子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Like a flute with no holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没错\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,供手指摆弄\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}For fingering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你够了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Would you stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以要是你搞砸了 就什么都锻造不出来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So when you blow it, nothing comes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,‎天啊 你这女人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Good god, woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我很无聊 吓唬你找点乐子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm bored, and it's fun to horrify you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,满足我吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Indulge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,‎然后想想怎么告诉卡米拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And think of something to tell Carmilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她会很生气的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}She's getting very cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎亲爱的 真遗憾\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, dear. How sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎别在意\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎说真的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你应该已经做了好几周魔法锤了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You've supposedly been making your magic hammer for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你就不能做个简单点的工具\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Couldn't you make something simpler?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:07:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,‎棍子 硬币 或者别的东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}A stick, or a coin, or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们都用不同的工具\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We all use different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,‎艾萨克用的是一把刀\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Isaac used a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎锤子更适合我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}A hammer works better for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好吧 那就快点做出来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, make it work faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎要是卡米拉发脾气\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}If Carmilla loses her temper,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我没办法站在你前面帮你挡很久\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I won't be able to stand in front of you for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你有站在我前面帮我挡吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You'd stand in front of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,‎已经挡了好几周了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've been doing it for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,‎嗯 好吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Huh. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 可不是嘛\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes, I suppose you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,‎谢谢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我在努力了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你知道我要说什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You know what I'm going to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎快点干\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Work faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是的 但是也要尽善尽美\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes, but it needs to be perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎否则什么都做不出来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}or nothing will come out of the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你真讨厌\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Ugh, you're disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‎赫克托做出该死的锤子了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Has Hector made his fucking hammer yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他还在努力\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He's still working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他在拖延时间\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He's stalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他很单纯 不会那样干的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He's too simple for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,‎-不是  ‎-不是吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- No. - No?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他身上有狡猾的气息\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There's a deviousness in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你竟然怀疑布娃娃\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Would you suspect a rag doll
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,打算偷你的钱包吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}of planning to steal your coin purse?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你误以为那只小狗温顺愚蠢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You mistake that puppy thing for being placid and stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他能杀人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He can kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他试过一次\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He tried, once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎充其量是不情愿\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It was half-hearted at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎看到了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Mm. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,‎看到什么 你当时不在场\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}See what? You weren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他很困惑 也很害怕\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He was confused and frightened,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎几乎不知道自己在做什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and barely even knew what he was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我是在提醒你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm warning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我只是提醒你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm just warning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎拜托 如果他这么危险 ‎德古拉会把他\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Please, would Dracula have kept him around in his own castle
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,‎留在自己的城堡里吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}if he were that dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我本来很喜欢那座城堡\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I would have liked that castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,‎德古拉的城堡吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Dracula's castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:09:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我没怎么看过那座城堡\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I didn't see a lot of it, in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我肯定里面\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But I'm sure it was full
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,满是有趣奇妙的东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}of interesting and wonderful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我必须得指出来 ‎你已经有一座漂亮的城堡了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am compelled to point out that you already have a nice castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎为什么想要他的城堡\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Why would you want his?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,‎因为我从愚蠢邪恶的老头手里抢东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Because I take things away from stupid, evil old men.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我就是干这个的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我一直都这么干\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've always done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们活该失去一切\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They deserve to lose everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,‎而我应该拥有他们所有的东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I deserve to have all their stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你可以创造新的东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You could just make new things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎如果我能抢走自己想要的东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Why would I waste my time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎然后杀了拥有这些东西的人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}when I can just take whatever I want
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎为什么还要浪费时间自己创造\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and then kill whoever had them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎看看我的地图\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Look at my map.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎从这里到布勒伊拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}From here to Braila.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那片土地和村镇属于老头\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That land and those villages and towns belong to old men.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,‎全都是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我要把它们抢过来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I'm going to take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这座城堡曾经属于 ‎一个愚蠢邪恶的老头\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This castle belonged to a stupid, evil old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我抢过来了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,‎从这里到布勒伊拉的土地\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The land from here to Braila,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,‎曾经掌控在愚蠢的老头手里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}ruled by stupid old men.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎毁在一个愚蠢的老头手里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Devastated by one single stupid old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,‎等着你下手\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There for the taking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你全抢过来就会开心吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And will you be happy when you have all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,‎看看这个\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Just look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你看\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你知道有多少地区的‎吸血鬼统治者死在布勒伊拉吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do you know how many regional vampire rulers died at Braila?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不知道我还要数人头\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I didn't know I had to count them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那你应该数一下\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎真不少\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It was a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这些只是我确定的数目\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}These are just the ones I'm certain of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这些小旗子吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}These little flags?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没错\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所有这些没有吸血鬼直接统治的地区\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All these regions without direct vampire rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎只等着有人来掌控\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Just waiting for someone to take control.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们的臣民肯定会推举一个人来统治\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Surely their underlings will raise someone up into command.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎除非我们先下手为强\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Unless we were there first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们为什么要这么做\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Why would we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这可是全世界 丽诺尔\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is the world, Lenore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:11:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们可以把全世界占为己有\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We could take the entire world for our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你不想这样吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Wouldn't you want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,‎装天真可爱这招对我可没用 丽诺尔\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The "sweet little girl" act doesn't work on me, Lenore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,‎再说一次\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我真的不知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我...我从来没有想过这么大的计划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I...I never thought about anything that big before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那就开始想吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,‎先回答我的问题\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Answer my question first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎拥有这一切\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Will you be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你会开心吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}when you have all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我人生的开端是男人夺走我的东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The first part of my life was men taking things from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,‎然后我夺去他们的性命\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And then I took their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,夺走他们的东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And their things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎占领他们的家园\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And their homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎然后我们占领了施第里尔\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And then we took Styria.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎后来 我们打造自己的小领地\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}After which we formed our little enclave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们尽量不造成更大的伤害\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We tried not to do more harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们努力建设家园\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We tried to make a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,‎然后狼人从北边打来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And when the wolf people came from the north,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎大军从西边进攻\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and the armies from the west,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所有的混蛋都来攻击我们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and every other bastard came for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们请求援助\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And we asked for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎吸血鬼世界的其他人当时怎么说的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What did the rest of the vampire world say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们说 "该死的女人"\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}"Bloody women," they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们说 "让她们去死"\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}"Let them die," they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以我要夺走所有人的一切\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So I'm going to take everything from everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我去过德古拉的城堡\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I was in Dracula's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我去那里 是看我能从中得到什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I went there to see what I could get out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎让自己拥有更多力量\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Get some more power for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎为我们带来更多保障\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Some more security for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我发现他和手下搞砸了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What I found was him and his people just fucking it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我在那里看到\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I saw, right there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我可以从他手里夺走全世界\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}that I could take the world away from him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,并据为己有\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and have it for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎全世界 丽诺尔\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The world, Lenore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我成功之后会开心吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Will I be happy when I've done that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不知道我是否在乎\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't know if I even care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我会拥有他们拥有的一切\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But I will have everything that they had.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们全都会死\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And they will all be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:13:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我会拥有我想要的全世界 ‎丽诺尔\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I will have the world I want, Lenore,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而这...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这就够了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}that will be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,‎拥有一切就够了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Having everything will be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎拥有全世界\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Having the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们全都死了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And all of them being dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一切都是为了这个吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Is this what it was all for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你觉得这是为了什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What on earth did you think this was all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想 他的锤子做好了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think he finished his hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好吧 在这里住一晚上\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, this won't be terrible,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,也不算糟糕\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}for one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你看 甚至还有‎迷人的窗户呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Look, it's even got an attractive window.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在屋顶上\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}In the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好极了 睡在星光下\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Perfect. Sleeping under starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,‎还会被鸟屎砸中\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And targeted by bird shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎从我们到这里 我就没见过一只鸟\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I haven't seen a single bird since we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎真的吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我能听到房梁上有动静\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I can hear something up in the rafters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎该死\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎又来了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Here we go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,‎尽量别把谷仓烧了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Try not to burn the barn down
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还在里面呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}while we're in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我只失手烧过一次\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I did that one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一次就够了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}One time was enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎上次有一只大蜘蛛\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It had a giant spider in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不是很大\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It wasn't giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,‎三米高啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It was ten feet tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也许才两米五\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Maybe eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以呢 两米五的蜘蛛难道不算大吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So, what, eight feet tall isn't giant?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:14:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Fuck me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,‎又是这些混蛋\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}These bastards again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们很厉害 不是吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They're very good, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们很烦人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They're annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也很年轻\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And young.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,‎很漂亮\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎皮肤光滑\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Smooth skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎怎么 你想下去为他们主持婚礼吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What, did you want to nip down there and marry them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想披上他们的皮\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I want to wear their skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你确定不想让我放火吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Are you sure you don't want me to set fire to things?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我现在觉得放火也许是个办法\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm thinking it might be an option now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,‎谢谢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们不知怎么掉进了这个圈套\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We somehow managed to walk right into that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不是冲你们来的 ‎这是给我们设的陷阱\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It wasn't for you. The trap was for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我是特雷弗·贝尔蒙特\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm Trevor Belmont.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是赛珐·贝尔纳德斯\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is Sypha Belnades.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.14,0:18:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎扎姆菲尔 塔哥维斯特地下宫廷的警卫队长\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Zamfir. Head guard to the Underground Court of Targoviste.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎德古拉第一次袭击后\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The ruling family of Targoviste
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎塔哥维斯特王室活了下来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}survived Dracula's first assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但后来吸血鬼和黑暗生物来了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But, later, the vampires and night creatures came,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎为了安全起见\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and it was safer to move them
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们躲进了城市地下的洞穴里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}into the catacombs under the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我很惊讶还有人活着\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm amazed anyone's still alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,更别说王室了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}let alone the royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我带领抵抗运动对抗恶魔\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I run the resistance against the devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,‎地狱也试图诅咒我们的黄金城\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Hell itself has attempted to curse our golden city,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我们不会屈服\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}but we will not allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我为你的手下感到遗憾\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm sorry about your people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们感谢你的帮助\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We are grateful for your aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们是为王室而死\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They died for the Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们确实是死了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, they did die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们是你的朋友 不是吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They were your friends, were they not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们一直在追查让德古拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We have been following signs of some plot
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,‎起死回生的阴谋迹象\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to return Dracula to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你了解这个情况吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Does this mean anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎城里有很多吸血鬼想这样做\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There's a nest of vampires in the city who wish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们想找到地下宫廷\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They are trying to find the Underground Court,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎掠夺数量众多的魔法宝藏 ‎用于他们的事业\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to ransack its many magical treasures for their cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们有兴趣参观这个宫廷\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We would be interested in seeing this court.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,‎以铲除这个隐患\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}To evaluate the threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们很高兴\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We would be delighted
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你们加入王室的战斗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to have you join the royal struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎很好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎帮助我们拯救塔哥维斯特\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Help us save Targoviste.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎很乐意\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Gladly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但现在还不行\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,‎等我确定可以信任你们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I cannot take you to the court
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,‎才能带你们进入宫廷\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}until I am certain I can trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎该死\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,‎她...很有意思\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, she was... interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你是说 有点疯狂吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You mean a little crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没错\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎可怜的家伙\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You poor bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,‎-你在做什么 ‎-没什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- What are you doing? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我知道你不会发死人财\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, I know you're not robbing the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎绝对不会\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我已经看够发光的石头了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I've seen enough glowing rocks for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,它们只会带来麻烦\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They lead to trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎说得很对\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Quite right too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要惹麻烦\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Why invite trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们从不惹麻烦\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We never do that.
